## CHANGELOG

- __2015/02/08__: 1.0.0 release.
    - Migrated from Bitbucket to GitHub.
    - Updated documentation as such, bumping up version to 1.0.0.

- __2014/12/17__: 0.5.0 release.
    - Enhanced handling for multi-line string input.
	- Minor documentation edits for clarity.

- __2014/12/14__: 0.4.0 release.
    - Very minor documentation corrections.

- __2014/12/14__: 0.3.0 release.
    - Slight enhancement to MIME encoded-word handling. 

- __2014/12/14__: 0.2.0 release.
    - Enhancements to deal with encoding marker.
	- Raise ArgumentError when non-UTF-7 encoding marker text is passed in.
	- Added more tests.

- __2014/12/13__: 0.1.0 release.
    - Initial release 
